short_summary: Replace 9 floating docks at Dauphin River, MB
description: The Contractor will be responsible for the following: 1. Supply and delivery of 6 (six) 1.219 X 6.096 finger float wharves to Dauphin River Harbour. 2. Supply and delivery of 3 (three) 1.829 X 6.096 principal float wharves to Dauphin River Harbour.
